 <span data-ttu-id="c85a6-156">Объект также может содержать <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsNameValueTag> объекты и <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsSemanticInterpretationTag> , которые добавляют семантические значения и семантические ключи к правилу. <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule></span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c85a6-156">An <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule> object may also contain <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsNameValueTag> and <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsSemanticInterpretationTag> objects that add semantic values and semantic keys to the rule.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c85a6-157">Модуль распознавания речи будет возвращать семантическую информацию, а также распознанную фразу, когда она распознает фразу.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c85a6-157">The speech recognition engine will return the semantic information, as well as the recognized phrase, when it recognizes the phrase.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c85a6-158">Дополнительные сведения см. в разделе [Разметка семантической интерпретации](https://docs.microsoft.com/previous-versions/office/developer/speech-technologies/hh361595(v%3doffice.14)) .</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c85a6-158">See [Semantic Interpretation Markup](https://docs.microsoft.com/previous-versions/office/developer/speech-technologies/hh361595(v%3doffice.14)) for more information.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="c85a6-159">В следующем примере создается грамматика, которая распознает фразу «страна, заключенная в жизнь мира», за которой следует имя страны, которая выиграл чашкой мира.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c85a6-159">The following example creates a grammar that recognizes the phrase "A nation that has won the World Cup is" followed by the name of a country that has won the World Cup.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c85a6-160">После создания <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule> объекта `winnerRule` и присвоения ему идентификатора `WorldCupWinner`строки в примере используется <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule.Add%2A> метод для добавления к правилу строки «страна, в которой заключена «чашка мира».</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c85a6-160">After creating the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule> object `winnerRule` and giving it the string identifier `WorldCupWinner`, the example uses the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule.Add%2A> method to append the string  "A nation that has won the World Cup is" to the rule.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c85a6-161">Затем в примере создаются два дополнительных правила: `ruleEurope` и `ruleSAmerica`.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c85a6-161">The example then creates two additional rules, `ruleEurope` and  `ruleSAmerica`.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c85a6-162">Опять же, <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule.Add%2A> используя метод, в примере к `WorldCupWinner` правилу, содержащему ссылки `ruleEurope` на правила, добавляются `ruleSAmerica` <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsOneOf> объекты и.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c85a6-162">Again using the <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule.Add%2A> method, the example appends an <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsOneOf> object to the `WorldCupWinner` rule that contains rule references to `ruleEurope` and `ruleSAmerica`.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
// Create an SrgsDocument, create a new rule  
// and set its scope to public.  
SrgsDocument document = new SrgsDocument();  
SrgsRule winnerRule = new SrgsRule("WorldCupWinner");  
winnerRule.Scope = SrgsRuleScope.Public;  
  
// Add the introduction.  
winnerRule.Elements.Add(new SrgsItem("A nation that has won the world cup is: "));  
  
// Create the rule for the European nations.  
SrgsOneOf oneOfEurope = new SrgsOneOf(new SrgsItem[] {new SrgsItem("England"), new SrgsItem("France"), new SrgsItem("Germany"), new SrgsItem("Italy")});  
SrgsRule ruleEurope = (new SrgsRule("EuropeanNations", new SrgsElement[] {oneOfEurope}));  
  
// Create the rule for the South American nations.  
SrgsOneOf oneOfSAmerica = new SrgsOneOf(new SrgsItem[] {new SrgsItem("Argentina"), new SrgsItem("Brazil"), new SrgsItem("Uruguay")});  
SrgsRule ruleSAmerica = (new SrgsRule("SouthAmericanNations", new SrgsElement[] {oneOfSAmerica}));  
  
// Add references to winnerRule for ruleEurope and ruleSAmerica.  
winnerRule.Elements.Add(new SrgsOneOf(new SrgsItem[] {(new SrgsItem (new SrgsRuleRef(ruleEurope))), new SrgsItem(new SrgsRuleRef(ruleSAmerica))}));  
  
// Add all the rules to the document and make winnerRule   
// the root rule of the document.  
document.Rules.Add(new SrgsRule[] {winnerRule, ruleEurope, ruleSAmerica});  
document.Root = winnerRule;  
```

  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="c85a6-192">Значение по умолчанию для scope `Private`равно.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c85a6-192">The default value for scope is `Private`.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c85a6-193">Закрытое правило может быть активировано только для распознавания ссылкой на правило из корневого правила в его содержащей грамматику или из другого правила, на которое ссылается корневое правило.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c85a6-193">A private rule can only be activated for recognition by a rule reference from the root rule in its containing grammar or from another rule that is referenced from the root rule.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c85a6-194">На частное правило не может ссылаться внешняя грамматика, если только закрытое правило не объявлено как корневое правило содержащего его грамматики.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c85a6-194">A private rule cannot be referenced by an external grammar, unless the private rule is declared as the root rule of its containing grammar.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="c85a6-195">Если его область имеет значение `Public` <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule> , объект может быть активирован для распознавания ссылкой из <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRuleRef> объекта в содержащей грамматику или из правила во внешней грамматике.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c85a6-195">If its scope is set to `Public`, an <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRule> object can be activated for recognition by a reference from a <xref:System.Speech.Recognition.SrgsGrammar.SrgsRuleRef> object in the containing grammar or from a rule in an external grammar.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="c85a6-196">В следующем примере создается грамматика, которая распознает фразу «страна, заключенная в жизнь мира», за которой следует имя страны, которая выиграл чашкой мира.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c85a6-196">The following example creates a grammar that recognizes the phrase "A nation that has won the World Cup is" followed by the name of a country that has won the World Cup.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="c85a6-197">Он создает открытое правило с `WorldCupWinner` именем и устанавливает область действия этого правила в значение Public.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c85a6-197">It creates a public rule named `WorldCupWinner` and sets the scope of that rule to Public.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
// Create an SrgsDocument, create a new rule and set its scope to public.  
SrgsDocument document = new SrgsDocument();  
SrgsRule winnerRule = new SrgsRule("WorldCupWinner");  
winnerRule.Scope = SrgsRuleScope.Public;  
  
// Add the introduction.  
winnerRule.Elements.Add(new SrgsItem("A nation that has won the world cup is: "));  
  
// Create the rule for the European nations.  
SrgsOneOf oneOfEurope = new SrgsOneOf(new SrgsItem[] {new SrgsItem("England"), new SrgsItem("France"), new SrgsItem("Germany"), new SrgsItem("Italy")});  
SrgsRule ruleEurope = (new SrgsRule("EuropeanNations", new SrgsElement[] {oneOfEurope}));  
  
// Create the rule for the South American nations.  
SrgsOneOf oneOfSAmerica = new SrgsOneOf(new SrgsItem[] {new SrgsItem("Argentina"), new SrgsItem("Brazil"), new SrgsItem("Uruguay")});  
SrgsRule ruleSAmerica = (new SrgsRule("SouthAmericanNations", new SrgsElement[] {oneOfSAmerica}));  
  
// Add references to winnerRule for ruleEurope and ruleSAmerica.  
winnerRule.Elements.Add(new SrgsOneOf(new SrgsItem[] {(new SrgsItem (new SrgsRuleRef(ruleEurope)), new SrgsItem(new SrgsRuleRef(ruleSAmerica)})));  
  
// Add all the rules to the document and make winnerRule   
// the root rule of the document.  
document.Rules.Add(new SrgsRule[] {winnerRule, ruleEurope, ruleSAmerica});  
document.Root = winnerRule;  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="c85a6-198">Созданная грамматика имеет следующую форму.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="c85a6-198">The created grammar has the following form.</span></span>  
  
```xml  
<grammar version="1.0" xml:lang="en-US" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2001/06/grammar" root="WorldCupWinner">  
    <rule id="WorldCupWinner" scope="public">  
        <item> A nation that has won the world cup is </item>  
        <one-of>  
            <item>  
                <ruleref uri="#EuropeanNations" />  
            </item>  
            <item>  
                <ruleref uri="#SouthAmericanNations" />  
            </item>  
        </one-of>  
    </rule>  
    <rule id="EuropeanNations">  
        <one-of>  
            <item> England< /item>  
            <item> France </item>  
            <item> Germany </item>  
            <item> Italy </item>  
        </one-of>  
    </rule>  
    <rule id="SouthAmericanNations">  
        <one-of>  
            <item> Argentina </item>  
            <item> Brazil </item>  
            <item> Uruguay </item>  
        </one-of>  
    </rule>  
</grammar>  
```
